  "title": "🚚 Driver (Full-Time) – $3000 to $3600 (OT + Incentives)",
  "description": "<p><strong>🚚 Cleaning Supervisor cum Driver (Full-Time) – $3000 to $3600 (OT + Incentives)</strong></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore</p><p><strong>Working Days:</strong> 6 days/week</p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 10:00am – 7:00pm (OT when required)</p><p><strong>Salary:</strong> $3000 – $3600 (with CPF) (OT Pay + Incentives)</p><p><br /></p><p>Doctor Clean Pte Ltd is looking for a reliable and responsible <u><strong>Cleaning Supervisor cum Driver</strong></u> to join our team! If you enjoy being on the move, working independently, and being part of a professional cleaning service team, we’d love to hear from you.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3><ul><li>Pick up and drop off equipment between locations</li><li>Transport staff to and from various job sites</li><li>Assist with simple upholstery cleaning tasks when required</li><li>Carry out basic supervisory duties on job sites when needed</li><li>Plan and manage daily routes independently</li><li>Carry out touchup cleaning when required</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3><ul><li>Valid Class 3 Driving License (able to drive manual vehicles)</li><li>Physically fit – able to carry loads up to 12kg</li><li>Able to speak and understand English</li><li>Professional appearance and conduct</li><li>Team player with a strong sense of responsibility</li></ul><h3><strong>Benefits:</strong></h3><ul><li>Van/Lorry can be driven home</li><li>Diesel and CashCard paid by company</li><li>Overtime pay and performance incentives</li><li>Friendly and supportive team environment</li></ul><p>📞 <strong>Apply Now!</strong>If you’re interested, send your resume to 96945012 / 81254781</p><p>Join us and be part of a company that values professionalism, teamwork, and growth!</p>",
